txt.en: 'There are many across the Sutcrofts who have been left homeless by the constant raids and assaults. These people have valuable skills and would be a good addition to our developing town. Not to mention, they need a new place to call home, and we do not leave our countrymen behind. We should begin to set up and prepare some tents to provide these people a place to live.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
